import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Typography,
  Grid,
  Button,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  Chip,
} from '@mui/material';
import {
  Edit as EditIcon,
  Print as PrintIcon,
  Download as DownloadIcon,
  ArrowBack as ArrowBackIcon,
} from '@mui/icons-material';
import { useParams, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';

interface PlanData {
  id: string;
  clientName: string;
  clientId: string;
  birthDate: string;
  gender: string;
  address: string;
  phone: string;
  emergencyContact: string;
  disabilityType: string;
  supportLevel: string;
  currentSituation: {
    livingSituation: string;
    physicalCondition: string;
    mentalCondition: string;
    socialParticipation: string;
    familySituation: string;
  };
  goals: {
    shortTerm: string;
    longTerm: string;
    achievementIndicators: string;
  };
  services: {
    serviceType: string;
    frequency: string;
    duration: string;
    provider: string;
    startDate: string;
  };
  supportSystem: {
    supportCoordinator: string;
    serviceProviders: string;
    relatedInstitutions: string;
    informalSupport: string;
  };
  monitoring: {
    frequency: string;
    evaluationMethod: string;
    reviewDate: string;
    emergencyResponse: string;
  };
  status: string;
  createdAt: string;
  updatedAt: string;
  assignedTo: string;
  education: string;
}

const PlanView: React.FC = () => {
  const { planId } = useParams<{ planId: string }>();
  const navigate = useNavigate();

  // ダミーデータ
  const planData: PlanData = {
    id: '1',
    clientName: '田中太郎',
    clientId: 'C001',
    birthDate: '1985-03-15',
    gender: '男性',
    address: '東京都渋谷区○○町1-2-3',
    phone: '03-1234-5678',
    emergencyContact: '田中花子（母） 090-1234-5678',
    disabilityType: '身体障害',
    supportLevel: '区分2',
    currentSituation: {
      livingSituation: '一人暮らし（アパート）',
      physicalCondition: '車椅子を使用、上肢に軽度の麻痺あり',
      mentalCondition: '安定している',
      socialParticipation: '地域のボランティア活動に参加',
      familySituation: '両親は健在、定期的に連絡',
    },
    goals: {
      shortTerm: '6ヶ月以内に自立した生活を送る',
      longTerm: '1年後に就労を目指す',
      achievementIndicators: '日常生活動作の自立度向上',
    },
    services: {
      serviceType: '居宅介護',
      frequency: '週3回',
      duration: '2時間/回',
      provider: '○○介護サービス',
      startDate: '2024-02-01',
    },
    supportSystem: {
      supportCoordinator: '山田相談員',
      serviceProviders: '○○介護サービス、△△医療センター',
      relatedInstitutions: '区役所福祉課、地域包括支援センター',
      informalSupport: '近隣住民、ボランティア',
    },
    monitoring: {
      frequency: '月1回',
      evaluationMethod: '面談、アンケート',
      reviewDate: '2024-07-01',
      emergencyResponse: '24時間対応可能',
    },
    status: '承認済み',
    createdAt: '2024-01-15',
    updatedAt: '2024-01-20',
    assignedTo: '山田相談員',
    education: '高卒',
  };

  const handleEdit = () => {
    navigate(`/editor/${planId}`);
  };

  const handlePrint = () => {
    window.print();
  };

  const handleDownload = () => {
    console.log('Downloading plan as PDF');
  };

  const getStatusColor = (status: string) => {
    switch (status) {
      case '承認済み':
        return 'success';
      case 'レビュー中':
        return 'warning';
      case '下書き':
        return 'default';
      default:
        return 'default';
    }
  };

  return (
    <Box>
      <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', mb: 3 }}>
        <Box>
          <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
            支援利用計画書
          </Typography>
          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 2 }}>
            <Typography variant="body1" color="textSecondary">
              利用者: {planData.clientName} ({planData.clientId})
            </Typography>
            <Chip
              label={planData.status}
              color={getStatusColor(planData.status) as any}
              size="small"
            />
          </Box>
        </Box>
        <Box>
          <Button
            startIcon={<ArrowBackIcon />}
            onClick={() => navigate('/plans')}
            sx={{ mr: 1 }}
          >
            戻る
          </Button>
          <Button
            startIcon={<EditIcon />}
            variant="contained"
            onClick={handleEdit}
            sx={{ mr: 1 }}
          >
            編集
          </Button>
          <Button
            startIcon={<PrintIcon />}
            onClick={handlePrint}
            sx={{ mr: 1 }}
          >
            印刷
          </Button>
          <Button
            startIcon={<DownloadIcon />}
            onClick={handleDownload}
          >
            PDF出力
          </Button>
        </Box>
      </Box>

      <Grid container spacing={3}>
        {/* 基本情報 */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                基本情報
              </Typography>
              <Grid container spacing={2}>
                <Grid item xs={6}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    氏名
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.clientName}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    生年月日
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.birthDate}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    性別
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.gender}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    電話番号
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.phone}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    住所
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.address}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    緊急連絡先
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.emergencyContact}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    障害種別
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.disabilityType}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    支援区分
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.supportLevel}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    最終学歴
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.education}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* 現状・アセスメント */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                現状・アセスメント
              </Typography>
              <Box sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                  現在の生活状況
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1">
                  {planData.currentSituation.livingSituation}
                </Typography>
              </Box>
              <Box sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                  身体機能・精神状態
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1">
                  {planData.currentSituation.physicalCondition}
                </Typography>
              </Box>
              <Box sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                  社会参加の状況
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1">
                  {planData.currentSituation.socialParticipation}
                </Typography>
              </Box>
              <Box>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                  家族・支援者の状況
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1">
                  {planData.currentSituation.familySituation}
                </Typography>
              </Box>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* 支援目標 */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                支援目標
              </Typography>
              <Grid container spacing={3}>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    短期目標（6ヶ月以内）
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.goals.shortTerm}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    長期目標（1年以上）
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.goals.longTerm}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    具体的な達成指標
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.goals.achievementIndicators}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* サービス利用計画 */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                サービス利用計画
              </Typography>
              <Grid container spacing={2}>
                <Grid item xs={6}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    利用サービス種別
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.services.serviceType}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    頻度
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.services.frequency}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    時間・期間
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.services.duration}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    利用開始予定日
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.services.startDate}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    提供事業者
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.services.provider}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* 支援体制 */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                支援体制
              </Typography>
              <Box sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                  相談支援事業者
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1">
                  {planData.supportSystem.supportCoordinator}
                </Typography>
              </Box>
              <Box sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                  サービス提供事業者
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1">
                  {planData.supportSystem.serviceProviders}
                </Typography>
              </Box>
              <Box sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                  関係機関・専門職
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1">
                  {planData.supportSystem.relatedInstitutions}
                </Typography>
              </Box>
              <Box>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                  家族・インフォーマル支援
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1">
                  {planData.supportSystem.informalSupport}
                </Typography>
              </Box>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* モニタリング計画 */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                モニタリング計画
              </Typography>
              <Grid container spacing={3}>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    モニタリング実施頻度
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.monitoring.frequency}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    評価方法・指標
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.monitoring.evaluationMethod}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    計画見直し予定日
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.monitoring.reviewDate}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    緊急時対応
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.monitoring.emergencyResponse}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* 管理情報 */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                管理情報
              </Typography>
              <Grid container spacing={3}>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    担当者
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.assignedTo}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    作成日
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.createdAt}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    更新日
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1">
                    {planData.updatedAt}
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                    ステータス
                  </Typography>
                  <Chip
                    label={planData.status}
                    color={getStatusColor(planData.status) as any}
                    size="small"
                  />
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default PlanView;
